      <title>FCC 称 AT&T 可用无线家用电话替代铜线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/at-t-can-substitute-wireless-home-phone-for-copper-fcc-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦通信委员会给美国电话电报公司 (AT&amp;T Inc.) 提前送上了一份圣诞礼物：允许其用新的无线固定电话技术取代旧的铜质家用电话线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/at-t-can-substitute-wireless-home-phone-for-copper-fcc-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 17:58:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
