      <title>MicroStrategy 连续第七周购买更多比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/microstrategy-buys-more-bitcoin-for-seventh-consecutive-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微策略公司 (MicroStrategy Inc.) 将于周一被纳入纳斯达克 100 指数，该公司宣布已以接近上周历史高点的平均价格额外购买了价值 5.61 亿美元的比特币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-23/microstrategy-buys-more-bitcoin-for-seventh-consecutive-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 13:21:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
